name: Professor T.
overview: Jasper Teerlinck, an eccentric professor, is an adviser to the police.

episodes.name: The Return
episodes.overview: Professor T consults on a campus rape case, identical to a decade-old incident in the same dorm.

episodes.name: The Payback
episodes.overview: A husband returns home to a grisly scene, and only Professor T can solve the brutal crime.

episodes.name: Hotel Murder
episodes.overview: Professor T unravels a mystery after a plastic surgeon is found murdered in his hotel room.

episodes.name: Tamara
episodes.overview: Professor T is implicated in the killing of a high-class call girl.

episodes.name: Masked Death
episodes.overview: Professor T investigates a ritual double murder.

episodes.name: The Lost Child
episodes.overview: Professor T discovers similarities to his own painful childhood while searching for a family’s missing son.

episodes.name: Bloodline
episodes.overview: After a brewery owner is found dead, Professor T learns every member of the victim’s family had a motive for murder.

episodes.name: Revenge
episodes.overview: Chief Inspector Rabe is the prime suspect in a double murder, and only Professor T can help him.
